location.fullValue: York Plan, Lake Margaret at The Highlands

data.description: Improved Price !!!  This gorgeous brick front home is on a remarkable and  1.4 acre corner lot, that provides plenty of open space, as well as privacy. Upon entering you will notice how meticulously kept this home has been. The kitchen features a double oven with stainless steel appliances, and granite counter tops. In addition to the living room and the dining room (with a view), the  downstairs rooms are very spacious and will provide you with lots of living space options to fit your lifestyle. i.e. an office, home gym, or library. You will love the wood stairs and the decorative stairway leading up to 4 immaculate bedrooms as well as generous sized laundry room. The Primary bedroom will amaze you with its very vast and impressive layout and the primary bathroom has an alluring garden tub and separate granite stand up shower. This amazing home, roof, HVAC, and appliances are 7 years new. Imagine living in an award winning community that features large lots, a golf course, a community pool, walking trails, a lovely lake, and is tucked away in a peaceful area of Chesterfield County. You can all of that and more in The Highlands.
